            . My brother Thomas is a <rs id="t18240407-134-viclabel750" type="occupation">cheesemonger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240407-134-victim1249 t18240407-134-viclabel750"></join>, and lives in <placeName id="t18240407-134-crimeloc751">Carnaby-street</placeName>
