                     <interp inst="t18240407-134-person1253" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I received him in charge. I have known him for five years; and until within the last month be has borne a good character.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was hired to carry it to Crown-court; the man who was with me carried my hat.</p>
               <p>
            
